high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the sink.
Take the knife in front of the sink.
Turn around, go forward to the left of the table, face the table.
Cut the closest apple on the table into pieces.
Turn right, go forward to the sink.
Put the knife in the cabinet to the bottom right of the sink.
Turn around, go back to the table with the cut apple.
Take a piece of apple from the table.
Turn right, go forward to the sink. Turn to the right.
Cook the apple in the microwave then take it out.
Turn left to the sink.
Put the piece of apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple in a sink.

high_descs: Turn around and face the sink in front of you.
Take the knife from the sink in front of you.
Turn around and face the table to your right.
Slice the apple on the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the cabinet by the sink in front of you.
Place the knife in the cabinet in front of you then close it.
Turn around and face the table to your right.
Take an apple slice from the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the microwave to your right.
Heat up the apple in the microwave then take it out.
Face the sink to your left.
Place the apple slice in the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a hot apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the sink
Pick up the knife in front of the sink
Turn around, go the table
Cut the apple on the table
Turn around, go to the sink
Put the knife in the cupboard to the right of the sink
Turn around, go the table
Pick up an apple piece from the table
Turn around, go to the sink, turn right to the microwave
Put the apple piece in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the apple piece from the microwave
Turn left to the sink
Put the apple piece in the sink
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple, cook a piece of the apple
